  <trk>
    <name>Ampola Storo Trail - Tour</name>
    <desc>The tour goes through the upper part of Valle di Ledro, climbs up to Malga Stigolo, descends to Lake Idro skirts the river Chiese and climbs back up to Valle di Ledro via Passo Giovo. A real up and down!</desc>
    <type>mountainbiking</type>
